works.description: We have seen some of the most radically designed, alluring and luxurious speakers to date, including the sexiest speakers you’d look on to hear long. The latest entrant to the ever-growing family of luxury speakers is the stunning range of omnidirectional loudspeakers from the French house SOEE Soundesign. The firm offers two models – Drop’s and Up’s - which comes in a range of alluring designs. While the Drop’s speakers are egg-shaped enclosures that can be placed on floor or furniture, the Up’s is a range of ceiling speaker with a unique design
